  "title": "Does psilocybin really provide long-term relief from depression, as new study suggests?",
  "text": "Psilocybin Single-dose psilocybin therapy shows promise for veterans with treatment-resistant depression November 5, 2024 A single dose of psilocybin significantly reduced depression symptoms in many U.S. veterans with treatment-resistant depression, with 60% showing improvement at three weeks. However, effects varied, and some experienced limited relief, highlighting the need for further research.\nRead more",
